videos.description: Jordan Ta'amu connects with A.J. Brown for 13 yards into the end zone to give Ole Miss an early lead.
videos.headline: Brown's TD puts Rebels on the board

videos.description: Breeland Speaks is ejected from the game for hitting Stephen Johnson helmet-to-helmet.
videos.headline: Ole Miss' Speaks ejected for targeting

videos.description: Benny Snell Jr. rushes for 2 yards into the end zone for a Kentucky TD in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Snell scores TD to put the Wildcats ahead

videos.description: Jordan Ta'amu finds Van Jefferson down the middle for a Rebels 20-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Jefferson's 20-yard TD puts Ole Miss back in the lead

videos.description: Benny Snell Jr. rushes for a 1-yard touchdown to give the Wildcats a lead going into halftime.
videos.headline: Snell's second TD of the day puts Kentucky ahead

videos.description: Kentucky head coach Mark Stoops discusses the adjustments they need to make coming into the second half.
videos.headline: Stoops: 'We've got to get some stops defensively'

videos.description: Stephen Johnson finds C.J. Conrad down the middle for a Wildcats' touchdown.
videos.headline: Kentucky's Conrad breaks free for a 46-yard TD

videos.description: Jordan Ta'amu finds D.K. Metcalf for 58 yards down the field for an Ole Miss touchdown late in the third quarter.
videos.headline: Metcalf's huge TD catch ties it for the Rebels

videos.description: Benny Snell Jr. puts the Wildcats back in the lead with a 1-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Kentucky's Snell rushes for 3rd TD today

videos.description: Jordan Ta'amu finds D.K. Metcalf for a 7-yard TD in the final seconds to lead the Rebels to a victory.
videos.headline: Ole Miss' Metcalf reaches over defender for huge game-winning catch

videos.description: Ole Miss head coach Matt Luke speaks on D.K. Metcalf's final play, QB Jordan Ta'amu's performance in his second start and the Rebels' 37-34 victory over UK.
videos.headline: Luke: Ta'amu impressive in 'gutsy win'
